ables.</span></h1><div class="h1-list"><div class="h1-list-item"><div class="square"></div><div class="text-14-regualr-caps" text-split-delay="8">Redéployer 3,5M TL depuis Sar Life</div></div><div class="h1-list-item"><div class="square"></div><div class="text-14-regualr-caps" text-split-delay="8">Viser 24k–34k TL de loyers mensuels</div></div><div class="h1-list-item"><div class="square"></div><div class="text-14-regualr-caps" text-split-delay="8">Réduire le risque avec deux locataires</div></div></div></div><div class="btns-wrap"><a class="btn-video w-inline-block" href="assets-rebuilt/5fc4c79219_video.html"><div class="btn-text-wrap"><div class="btn-arrow-wrapper"><svg fill="none" viewbox="0 0 18 18" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.4031 8.20312C11.6283 8.20312 11.8179 8.28016 11.972 8.43424C12.1261 8.58831 12.2031 8.77794 12.2031 9.00312C12.2031 9.22831 12.1261 9.41794 11.972 9.57201C11.8179 9.72609 11.6283 9.80312 11.4031 9.80312C11.1779 9.80312 10.9883 9.72609 10.8342 9.57201C10.6802 9.41794 10.6031 9.22831 10.6031 9.00312C10.6031 8.77794 10.6802 8.58831 10.8342 8.43424C10.9883 8.28016 11.1779 8.20312 11.4031 8.20312Z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M8.60469 5.60156C8.82987 5.60156 9.0195 5.6786 9.17358 5.83267C9.32765 5.98675 9.40469 6.17637 9.40469 6.40156C9.40469 6.62674 9.32765 6.81638 9.17358 6.97045C9.0195 7.12453 8.82987 7.20156 8.60469 7.20156C8.3795 7.20156 8.18987 7.12453 8.0358 6.97045C7.88172 6.81638 7.80469 6.62674 7.80469 6.40156C7.80469 6.17637 7.88172 5.98675 8.0358 5.83267C8.18987 5.6786 8.3795 5.60156 8.60469 5.60156Z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M8.60469 8C8.82987 8 9.0195 8.07704 9.17358 8.23111C9.32765 8.38519 9.40469 8.57481 9.40469 8.8C9.40469 9.02518 9.32765 9.21482 9.17358 9.36889C9.0195 9.52296 8.82987 9.59999 8.60469 9.59999C8.3795 9.59999 8.18987 9.52296 8.0358 9.36889C7.88172 9.21482 7.80469 9.02518 7.80469 8.8C7.80469 8.57481 7.88172 8.38519 8.0358 8.23111C8.18987 8.07704 8.3795 8 8.60469 8