s-rebuilt/efe9b3cd01_6879f874f1b00e4d0dfc1cdb_image%201990-p-500.webp 500w, assets-rebuilt/45497b44d7_6879f874f1b00e4d0dfc1cdb_image%201990-p-800.webp 800w, assets-rebuilt/ad1e2bfc14_6879f874f1b00e4d0dfc1cdb_image%201990-p-1080.webp 1080w, assets-rebuilt/d9d13afbde_6879f874f1b00e4d0dfc1cdb_image%201990-p-1600.webp 1600w, assets-rebuilt/9f9c760520_6879f874f1b00e4d0dfc1cdb_image%201990-p-2000.webp 2000w, assets-rebuilt/3c1d7c3449_6879f874f1b00e4d0dfc1cdb_image%201990.webp 2518w"/></div></div></div></div></div><div class="nav-sidebar"><a class="link-block w-inline-block" data-w-id="bbdca07a-6c5c-7c8f-3509-f05b9cfedfdd" href="#design-section"><div class="text-block-3">DESIGN</div></a><a class="link-block estimate w-inline-block" href="#estimate-section"><div class="text-block-3">estimate</div></a><a class="link-block shop w-inline-block" href="#shop-section"><div class="text-block-3">shop</div></a></div><div class="design-nav-sensor"><div class="design-onpage-link" id="design-section"></div><div class="design-container _1" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7776"><div class="design-camera" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7777"><div class="design-title-wrap" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7778"><h2 class="text-52-regular heading-slider" text-split-delay="1,5">Pourquoi <br/>Future Park ?</h2></div><div class="in-animation-box" data-w-id="c16581ae-4351-c616-11e6-827240158ae7"><div class="design-wrap _1"><div class="slide-content _1"><div class="slide-1-grid"><div class="slide-1-grid-1 align-bottom" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7780"><div class="lottie-animation" data-animation-type="lottie" data-autoplay="0" data-direction="1" data-duration="0" data-is-ix2-target="1" data-ix2-initial-state="0" data-loading="eager" data-loop="0" data-renderer="svg" data-src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e/6852bb69c309879bb29af3ab_pinmap_j.json" data-w-id="267a16d6-1048-eaf5-5275-22e7620c4c84"></div><img alt="" class="google-img" loading="eager" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" src="assets-rebuilt/3b03b71f05_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325.png" srcset="assets-rebuilt/2e21ad2670_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325-p-500.png 500w, assets-rebuilt/f5956cc6e7_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325-p-800.png 800w, assets-rebuilt/5d155a9335_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325-p-1080.png 1080w, assets-rebuilt/3b03b71f05_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325.png 1252w"/><h3 class="text-30-regular">Conçu pour le séjour flexible</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Le format hôtel-résidence de Future Park convient naturellement aux séjours meublés, patients médicaux, accompagnateurs et résidents temporaires.</div></div><div class="slide-2-grid-2"><div class="gap-8 limit-50"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Prix décoté, usage réel</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">La réputation fragilisée crée une décote, mais les unités habitables répondent déjà à une vraie demande locative à Istanbul.</div></div><div class="video-1 w-background-video w-background-video-atom" data-autoplay="true" data-loop="true" data-poster-url="assets-rebuilt/e05ebeb571_6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e_682b2eba39afea9d091faa50_1-poster-00001.jpg" data-video-urls="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2eba39afea9d091faa50_1-transcode.mp4,https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2eba39afea9d091faa50_1-transcode.webm" data-wf-ignore="true"><a class="video-placeholder-link" href="assets-rebuilt/5fc4c79219_video2.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><img alt="Ouvrir la video" class="video-placeholder-image" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/placeholder.png"/></a></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1 align-bottom"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Rendement des petites surfaces</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Les studios et 1+0 transforment un capital limité en cash-flow plus fort qu’un grand appartement classique.</div><div class="design-camera-absolut"><div class="camera-control-img-grid single-camera-image"><div class="img-hover"><img alt="" class="camera-control-placeholder" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/1.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1 align-bottom extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><div class="lottie-animation" data-animation-type="lottie" data-autoplay="0" data-direction="1" data-duration="0" data-is-ix2-target="1" data-ix2-initial-state="0" data-loading="eager" data-loop="0" data-renderer="svg" data-src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e/6852bb69c309879bb29af3ab_pinmap_j.json"></div><img alt="" class="google-img" loading="eager" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" src="assets-rebuilt/3b03b71f05_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325.png" srcset="assets-rebuilt/2e21ad2670_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325-p-500.png 500w, assets-rebuilt/f5956cc6e7_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325-p-800.png 800w, assets-rebuilt/5d155a9335_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325-p-1080.png 1080w, assets-rebuilt/3b03b71f05_685312d28646ac27e1e57f46_Frame%202131330325.png 1252w"/><h3 class="text-30-regular">Compatible séjour médical</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Les patients préfèrent souvent un appartement privé : cuisine, intimité, calme, accompagnateur, récupération confortable et séjour prolongé.</div></div><div class="slide-2-grid-2 extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><div class="gap-8 limit-50"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Avantage propriétaire-opérateur</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Quatre ans d’expérience clinique, réseau local et accès direct aux invités créent une demande que l’investisseur passif n’a pas.</div></div><div class="video-1 w-background-video w-background-video-atom" data-autoplay="true" data-loop="true" data-poster-url="assets-rebuilt/e05ebeb571_6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e_682b2eba39afea9d091faa50_1-poster-00001.jpg" data-video-urls="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2eba39afea9d091faa50_1-transcode.mp4,https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2eba39afea9d091faa50_1-transcode.webm" data-wf-ignore="true"><a class="video-placeholder-link" href="assets-rebuilt/5fc4c79219_video2.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><img alt="Ouvrir la video" class="video-placeholder-image" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/placeholder.png"/></a></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1 align-bottom extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Services à forte valeur</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Transferts, taxis, courses, livraisons, traduction, assistance locale et packages touristiques augmentent l’expérience et le revenu potentiel.</div><div class="design-camera-absolut"><div class="camera-control-img-grid single-camera-image"><div class="img-hover"><img alt="" class="camera-control-placeholder" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/1.png"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide-content _2"><div class="slide-1-grid"><div class="slide-1-grid-1" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7797"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Maîtrise locale</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Résider à Istanbul et connaître les règles locales réduit les risques d’exécution : gestion, administration, invités et structuration locative.</div><div class="apartmen-img-wrapper"><img alt="" class="apartment-img _1" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c779c" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/4f32581370_6851b5afa8312a49891754de_Group%20989.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _2" data-w-id="38de498b-e524-02f5-2f71-bc183cf9adf4" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/a2eea2e42c_6851b5afac7e655b4df00710_Group%20990.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _3" data-w-id="a43fc409-f6e6-8b06-6774-1ed2b2edc43e" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/52dab163cc_6851b5af41af6a3b879de6ff_Group%201028.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _4" data-w-id="04aa313a-047e-d993-003c-93fa4051cf0b" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/b9dbfd6b24_6851b5af2792391b144798bf_Group%201029.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _5" data-w-id="f868cfe0-3854-aa7e-4db9-1fee203f4eca" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/d5a56e3eec_6851b5af2d7b09035d1aef7e_Group%201030.png"/></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-2"><div class="video-1 w-background-video w-background-video-atom" data-autoplay="true" data-loop="true" data-poster-url="assets-rebuilt/2fff374db3_6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e_682b2b1c0d8cb6f1970b6e32_2%20_2_-poster-00001.jpg" data-video-urls="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2b1c0d8cb6f1970b6e32_2%20%282%29-transcode.mp4,https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2b1c0d8cb6f1970b6e32_2%20%282%29-transcode.webm" data-wf-ignore="true"><a class="video-placeholder-link" href="assets-rebuilt/5fc4c79219_video3.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><img alt="Ouvrir la video" class="video-placeholder-image" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/placeholder.png"/></a></div><div class="gap-8"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Option de revalorisation</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Si l’hôtel ou les parties commerciales sont relancés, les unités achetées aujourd’hui avec décote peuvent bénéficier d’un changement de perception.</div></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c77a4"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Le downside reste viable</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Même sans renaissance complète du projet, l’unité peut fonctionner en location meublée mensuelle, portée par le cash-flow plutôt que la spéculation.</div><div class="point-img-wrapper"><img alt="" class="poi-bg _1" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c77a9" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/933f3d11c7_6851c347b8e04f765a40c947_Property%201_1.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _2" data-w-id="ef87bbd6-e7c4-3276-1021-a459e677ac76" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/063ebdcc7f_6851c34782209d523067dd3a_Property%201_2.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _3" data-w-id="6bc99703-0cdf-225b-e6fe-9b959a15e1e7" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/b3138ee217_6851c348ea029903a38106bb_Property%201_3.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _4" data-w-id="98010ec8-fc68-c500-998e-b6a0361c55b8" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/6a3779f894_6851c347c9ecd00dd26b9faf_Property%201_4.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _5" data-w-id="abc42d01-37f0-c934-df5f-8178253662f7" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/8c71d664cc_6851c34896860f893f0c7d95_Property%201_5.webp"/></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1 extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><h3 class="text-30-regular">À vérifier avant achat</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Le potentiel doit être confirmé : tapu, bloc habitable, aidat réel, règles de résidence, accès invités et rentabilité nette.</div><div class="apartmen-img-wrapper"><img alt="" class="apartment-img _1" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/4f32581370_6851b5afa8312a49891754de_Group%20989.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _2" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/a2eea2e42c_6851b5afac7e655b4df00710_Group%20990.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _3" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/52dab163cc_6851b5af41af6a3b879de6ff_Group%201028.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _4" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/b9dbfd6b24_6851b5af2792391b144798bf_Group%201029.png"/><img alt="" class="apartment-img _5" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/d5a56e3eec_6851b5af2d7b09035d1aef7e_Group%201030.png"/></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-2 extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><div class="video-1 w-background-video w-background-video-atom" data-autoplay="true" data-loop="true" data-poster-url="assets-rebuilt/2fff374db3_6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e_682b2b1c0d8cb6f1970b6e32_2%20_2_-poster-00001.jpg" data-video-urls="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2b1c0d8cb6f1970b6e32_2%20%282%29-transcode.mp4,https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a2e%2F682b2b1c0d8cb6f1970b6e32_2%20%282%29-transcode.webm" data-wf-ignore="true"><a class="video-placeholder-link" href="assets-rebuilt/5fc4c79219_video3.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><img alt="Ouvrir la video" class="video-placeholder-image" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/placeholder.png"/></a></div><div class="gap-8"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Demande non dépendante d’Airbnb</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Le modèle repose d’abord sur un réseau clinique et des séjours meublés, pas uniquement sur les plateformes touristiques.</div></div></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1 extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><h3 class="text-30-regular">Un actif à opérer</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Future Park devient intéressant parce qu’il peut être exploité activement : logement, service, accompagnement et marketing ciblé.</div><div class="point-img-wrapper"><img alt="" class="poi-bg _1" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/933f3d11c7_6851c347b8e04f765a40c947_Property%201_1.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _2" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/063ebdcc7f_6851c34782209d523067dd3a_Property%201_2.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _3" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/b3138ee217_6851c348ea029903a38106bb_Property%201_3.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _4" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/6a3779f894_6851c347c9ecd00dd26b9faf_Property%201_4.webp"/><img alt="" class="poi-bg _5" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/8c71d664cc_6851c34896860f893f0c7d95_Property%201_5.webp"/></div></div></div></div></div><div class="design-pagination-wrapper"><div class="design_circle-wrapper"><div class="design_circle _1"></div><div class="design_circle _2"></div><div class="design_circle _3"></div><div class="design_circle _4"></div><div class="design_circle _5"></div><div class="design_circle _6"></div></div></div></div><a class="btn-to-top w-inline-block" href="#design-section"><div class="btn-to-top-arrow-wrap"><svg class="svg" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 12 14" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M0.112362 6.26535C0.0743662 6.30776 0.0449248 6.35739 0.0257187 6.41141C0.00651258 6.46544 -0.00208211 6.52279 0.000425491 6.58021C0.00293309 6.63762 0.0164938 6.69397 0.0403334 6.74603C0.064173 6.7981 0.0978245 6.84486 0.139367 6.88365C0.223265 6.96198 0.33421 7.00309 0.447796 6.99792C0.504038 6.99536 0.559235 6.98151 0.610236 6.95718C0.661237 6.93284 0.707043 6.89849 0.745039 6.85608L5.57241 1.4581V13.5624C5.57241 13.6785 5.61758 13.7898 5.69796 13.8718C5.77835 13.9539 5.88737 14 6.00106 14C6.11474 14 6.22377 13.9539 6.30415 13.8718C6.38454 13.7898 6.4297 13.6785 6.4297 13.5624V1.46073L11.2545 6.85608C11.2924 6.89855 11.3382 6.93297 11.3892 6.95738C11.4401 6.98179 11.4953 6.99571 11.5516 6.99836C11.6078 7.001 11.664 6.9923 11.717 6.97277C11.7699 6.95324 11.8186 6.92325 11.8602 6.88452C11.9018 6.84579 11.9355 6.79908 11.9594 6.74704C11.9833 6.69501 11.997 6.63868 11.9995 6.58126C12.0021 6.52385 11.9936 6.46648 11.9745 6.41242C11.9554 6.35837 11.926 6.30869 11.888 6.26622L6.47514 0.213626C6.40724 0.137764 6.32284 0.0792358 6.22873 0.0427545C6.13463 0.00627322 6.03344 -0.00714206 5.93333 0.00358846C5.7767 0.0202251 5.6315 0.0949623 5.52526 0.213626L0.112362 6.26535Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></a></div></div><div class="design-container _2" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c77aa" id="design-2"><div class="design-camera" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c77ab"><div class="design-title-wrap" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c77ac"><h2 class="text-52-regular heading-slider" text-split="">Meublé,<br/>flexible</h2></div><div class="design-2-animation"><div class="design-wrap _2"><div class="slide-content _1"><div class="slide-1-grid"><div class="slide-1-grid-1" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7797"><a class="evidence-card-link" href="https://www.sahibinden.com/satilik?query_text=Future+Park+Esenyurt" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<div class="evidence-shot-wrap"><img alt="Recherche Future Park en direct" class="evidence-shot" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/evidence/sahibinden-future-park-satilik-2026-05-28.png"/></div>
<div class="evidence-copy">
<div class="evidence-kicker">PREUVE VENTE</div>
<h3 class="text-30-regular evidence-title">Recherche Future Park en direct</h3>
<div class="text-14-regular opacity-60 evidence-body">Les annonces Future Park 1+0/studio montrent une fourchette exploitable autour de 1,30M-1,45M TL. C’est la base de la stratégie : acheter petit, garder une réserve, louer vite.</div>
<div class="evidence-metrics"><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Fourchette</span><strong>1.30M-1.45M TL</strong></div><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Cible</span><strong>1+0 / studio</strong></div></div>
<div class="evidence-open">Ouvrir la recherche vente ↗</div>
</div>
</a></div><div class="slide-1-grid-2"><a class="evidence-card-link" href="https://www.sahibinden.com/ilan/emlak-konut-satilik-future-parkta-site-icinde-temiz-ve-ferah-satilik-1-plus0-daire-1305084976/detay" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<div class="evidence-shot-wrap"><img alt="1+0 Future Park vérifié" class="evidence-shot" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/evidence/sahibinden-detail-future-park-sale-1305084976-2026-05-28.png"/></div>
<div class="evidence-copy">
<div class="evidence-kicker">DÉTAIL CAPTURÉ</div>
<h3 class="text-30-regular evidence-title">1+0 Future Park vérifié</h3>
<div class="text-14-regular opacity-60 evidence-body">Détail capturé : 55/40 m2, 7e étage, aidat 1 750 TL. Même au haut de fourchette, deux unités restent finançables avec une réserve de trésorerie.</div>
<div class="evidence-metrics"><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Prix</span><strong>1.45M TL</strong></div><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Aidat</span><strong>1,750 TL</strong></div></div>
<div class="evidence-open">Ouvrir le détail ↗</div>
</div>
</a></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c77a4"><a class="evidence-card-link" href="https://www.sahibinden.com/kiralik-daire?query_text=Future+Park+Esenyurt" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<div class="evidence-shot-wrap"><img alt="Loyers 1+0 observés" class="evidence-shot" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/evidence/sahibinden-future-park-kiralik-2026-05-28.png"/></div>
<div class="evidence-copy">
<div class="evidence-kicker">PREUVE LOYER</div>
<h3 class="text-30-regular evidence-title">Loyers 1+0 observés</h3>
<div class="text-14-regular opacity-60 evidence-body">Les résultats de location Future Park affichent des studios autour de 12k-15k TL/mois. Deux unités donnent une cible combinée de 24k-30k TL avant optimisation.</div>
<div class="evidence-metrics"><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Loyer/unité</span><strong>12k-15k TL</strong></div><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Deux unités</span><strong>24k-30k TL/mois</strong></div></div>
<div class="evidence-open">Ouvrir la recherche location ↗</div>
</div>
</a></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1 extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><a class="evidence-card-link" href="https://www.sahibinden.com/satilik?query_text=Future+Park+Esenyurt" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<div class="evidence-shot-wrap"><img alt="Deux achats restent sous contrôle" class="evidence-shot" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/evidence/sahibinden-future-park-satilik-2026-05-28.png"/></div>
<div class="evidence-copy">
<div class="evidence-kicker">PLAN CAPITAL</div>
<h3 class="text-30-regular evidence-title">Deux achats restent sous contrôle</h3>
<div class="text-14-regular opacity-60 evidence-body">Avec 3,5M TL issus de Sar Life, deux achats Future Park laissent encore une réserve pour frais, ameublement et imprévus. Le risque passe d’un seul actif à deux petites sorties.</div>
<div class="evidence-metrics"><div class="evidence-metric"><span>2 × 1.30M</span><strong>550k TL réserve</strong></div><div class="evidence-metric"><span>2 × 1.45M</span><strong>250k TL réserve</strong></div></div>
<div class="evidence-open">Comparer les ventes ↗</div>
</div>
</a></div><div class="slide-1-grid-2 extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><a class="evidence-card-link" href="https://www.sahibinden.com/ilan/emlak-konut-kiralik-e5-e-yakin-future-park-1-plus0-kiralik-daire-akilli-ev-konsepti-1311110867/detay" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<div class="evidence-shot-wrap"><img alt="Mensuel stable ou court séjour" class="evidence-shot" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/evidence/sahibinden-future-park-kiralik-2026-05-28.png"/></div>
<div class="evidence-copy">
<div class="evidence-kicker">SCÉNARIO REVENU</div>
<h3 class="text-30-regular evidence-title">Mensuel stable ou court séjour</h3>
<div class="text-14-regular opacity-60 evidence-body">Le plan prioritaire reste mensuel stable. Le court séjour type Airbnb devient une option seulement si règlement, gestion et demande locale le permettent.</div>
<div class="evidence-metrics"><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Mensuel</span><strong>base 12k-15k</strong></div><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Court séjour</span><strong>option à vérifier</strong></div></div>
<div class="evidence-open">Voir un exemple loyer ↗</div>
</div>
</a></div><div class="slide-1-grid-1 extra-grid-slot" data-extra-grid-slot="true"><a class="evidence-card-link" href="https://www.sahibinden.com/ilan/emlak-konut-satilik-future-parkta-site-icinde-temiz-ve-ferah-satilik-1-plus0-daire-1305084976/detay" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<div class="evidence-shot-wrap"><img alt="Le produit locatif central" class="evidence-shot" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/evidence/sahibinden-detail-future-park-sale-1305084976-2026-05-28.png"/></div>
<div class="evidence-copy">
<div class="evidence-kicker">FUTURE</div>
<h3 class="text-30-regular evidence-title">Le produit locatif central</h3>
<div class="text-14-regular opacity-60 evidence-body">C'est l'idée centrale : une résidence moderne, compacte et équipée peut devenir un produit locatif plus souple qu'un grand appartement classique.</div>
<div class="evidence-metrics"><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Objectif</span><strong>souplesse locative</strong></div><div class="evidence-metric"><span>Décision</span><strong>vérifier puis agir</strong></div></div>
<div class="evidence-open">Revoir la preuve clé ↗</div>
</div>
</a></div></div></div><div class="slide-content _3"><div class="slide-1-grid"><div class="slide-1-grid-1 align-bottom"><div class="div-block-27"></div><h3 class="text-30-regular">Ameublement <br/>prêt à louer</h3><div class="text-14-regular opacity-60">Un studio bien équipé peut être préparé <br/>rapidement pour un locataire ou un voyageur.</div><div class="tabs w-tabs" data-current="Tab 1" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" data-easing="ease-in-cubic"><div class="tabs-menu w-tab-menu"><a class="tab-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" data-w-tab="Tab 1"><div class="btn-text-wrap"><div class="btn-text">Studio</div></div></a><a class="tab-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" data-w-tab="Tab 2"><div class="btn-text-wrap"><div class="btn-text">Couple</div></div></a><a class="tab-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" data-w-tab="Tab 3"><div class="btn-text-wrap"><div class="btn-text">Famille</div></div></a></div><div class="tabs-content w-tab-content"><div class="tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" data-w-tab="Tab 1"><div class="pre-design-tabcontent"><img alt="" class="pre-diesgn-bg-img" loading="eager" src="assets-rebuilt/352f6154c3_68485417567fa5ec93cb26fc_cc2979e89ddfdcaf6b808aaf41916559d70af0f4.webp"/><div class="gradient-tab"><img alt="" class="pre-design-scheme" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="assets-rebuilt/ee31290961_685394cd3145eae191ad5f92_img.png" srcset="assets-rebuilt/2b7030679a_685394cd3145eae191ad5f92_img-p-500.png 500w, assets-rebuilt/ee31290961_685394cd3145eae191ad5f92_img.png 557w"/><div class="pre-design-scheme-code hide w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="144" viewbox="0 0 140 144" width="140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
