class="tab-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" data-w-tab="Tab 1"><div class="btn-text-wrap"><div class="btn-text">stable</div></div></a><a class="tab-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" data-w-tab="Tab 2"><div class="btn-text-wrap"><div class="btn-text">flexible</div></div></a></div><div class="tabs-content w-tab-content"><div class="tab-pane w-tab-pane" data-w-tab="Tab 1"><div class="pre-design-tabcontent"><div class="gradient-tab"><img alt="" class="pre-design-scheme floor" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="assets-rebuilt/1d83557ab9_6853971ca951a0c15ea39071_img%20_1_.png" srcset="assets-rebuilt/025c3133c4_6853971ca951a0c15ea39071_img%20_1_-p-500.png 500w, assets-rebuilt/e4141a5fb4_6853971ca951a0c15ea39071_img%20_1_-p-800.png 800w, assets-rebuilt/9903d2253b_6853971ca951a0c15ea39071_img%20_1_-p-1080.png 1080w, assets-rebuilt/002178249d_6853971ca951a0c15ea39071_img%20_1_-p-1600.png 1600w, assets-rebuilt/89e4724f31_6853971ca951a0c15ea39071_img%20_1_-p-2000.png 2000w, assets-rebuilt/1d83557ab9_6853971ca951a0c15ea39071_img%20_1_.png 2232w"/></div></div></div><div class="tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" data-w-tab="Tab 2"><div class="pre-design-tabcontent"><div class="gradient-tab"><img alt="" class="pre-design-scheme floor" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="assets-rebuilt/398904d805_68539730d263de805bfaa738_img%20_2_.png" srcset="assets-rebuilt/9f5889c8d8_68539730d263de805bfaa738_img%20_2_-p-500.png 500w, assets-rebuilt/fdab3002b9_68539730d263de805bfaa738_img%20_2_-p-800.png 800w, assets-rebuilt/0cd68206e9_68539730d263de805bfaa738_img%20_2_-p-1080.png 1080w, assets-rebuilt/fdc956abc7_68539730d263de805bfaa738_img%20_2_-p-1600.png 1600w, assets-rebuilt/3f8be616b0_68539730d263de805bfaa738_img%20_2_-p-2000.png 2000w, assets-rebuilt/398904d805_68539730d263de805bfaa738_img%20_2_.png 2232w"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide-content daynight"><div class="day-light-images"><img alt="" class="night-image" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="as