oading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/750cc3f65c_682b2208a9fb2fa8fa659d03_dot.svg"/></div></div><div class="estimate-card-item"><div class="furniture-wrap"><img alt="" class="furniture-img" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/7724245e80_6879f4078c713cf6fe6f1491_img-2.avif"/><div class="text-14-regular black">Bloom S5 lamp</div></div><div class="radio-wrap" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db20f5-75768a4d"><div class="text-14-regular black">1,760 €</div><img alt="" class="radio" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db20f8-75768a4d" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/750cc3f65c_682b2208a9fb2fa8fa659d03_dot.svg"/></div></div><div class="estimate-card-item"><div class="furniture-wrap"><img alt="" class="furniture-img" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/3e14daa452_6879f407779cc03c5606079a_img-1.avif"/><div class="text-14-regular black">Totem floor lamp</div></div><div class="radio-wrap" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db20fe-75768a4d"><div class="text-14-regular black">1,850 €</div><img alt="" class="radio" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db2101-75768a4d" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/750cc3f65c_682b2208a9fb2fa8fa659d03_dot.svg"/></div></div><div class="estimate-card-item"><div class="furniture-wrap"><img alt="" class="furniture-img" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/df3257a4ff_6879f4072453787cd298c178_img-3.avif"/><div class="text-14-regular black">Wool rug</div></div><div class="radio-wrap" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db2107-75768a4d"><div class="text-14-regular black">60 €</div><img alt="" class="radio" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db210a-75768a4d" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/750cc3f65c_682b2208a9fb2fa8fa659d03_dot.svg"/></div></div><div class="estimate-card-item"><div class="furniture-wrap"><img alt="" class="furniture-img" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/d645a99d2e_6879f4072d1db1bc3699bb3f_img-4.avif"/><div class="text-14-regular black">Kasper dining table</div></div><div class="radio-wrap" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db2110-75768a4d"><div class="text-14-regular black">2,300 €</div><img alt="" class="radio" id="w-node-_500bca71-53d9-846a-ea17-eaa5a4db2113-75768a4d" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/750cc3f65c_682b2208a9fb2fa8fa659d03_dot.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sensor-3in1-out"></div></div></section><section class="section-benefit" id="benefit"><div class="benefit-wrap" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c78b7"><div class="camera-benefit"><div class="benefit-heading-wrap"><h2 class="text-32-caps benefits color-gray">Points clés </h2><div class="div-block-16"><h2 class="text-32-caps benefits _1"><span class="color-gray">pour </span>l'investisseur</h2><h2 class="text-32-caps benefits absolut"><span class="color-gray">pour</span> Future Park</h2></div></div><div class="benefit-container"><div class="benefit-space"></div><div class="benefit-item"><div class="benefit-border"><div class="benefit-card"><h1 class="text-32-caps _2">Cash-flow plus flexible</h1><div class="text-16-white">Deux petites unités peuvent créer un revenu plus réparti qu'un seul grand appartement.</div></div></div></div><div class="benefit-item _2"><div class="benefit-border"><div class="benefit-card _2"><h1 class="text-32-caps _2">Capital mieux divisé</h1><div class="text-16-white">Le risque n'est plus bloqué dans un seul locataire, une seule vente ou une seule décision.</div></div></div></div><div class="benefit-item _3"><div class="benefit-border" data-w-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c78d6"><div class="benefit-card"><h1 class="text-32-caps _2">Location plus simple</h1><div class="text-16-white">Un studio meublé parle à plus de profils : seul, couple, court séjour ou location mensuelle.</div></div></div></div><div class="benefit-item _4"><div class="benefit-border _1"><div class="benefit-card _2"><h1 class="text-32-caps _2">Vérification obligatoire</h1><div class="text-16-white">Le potentiel existe seulement si le titre, l'aidat, l'état du bloc et la gestion sont confirmés.</div></div></div></div><div class="benefit-item _5"><div class="benefit-border"><div class="benefit-card"><h1 class="text-32-caps _2">Produit locatif moderne</h1><div class="text-16-white">Résidence, services, parking, Wi-Fi et smart features donnent une valeur d'usage plus forte.</div></div></div></div><div class="benefit-item _6"><div class="benefit-border _1"><div class="benefit-card _2"><h1 class="text-32-caps _2">Décision plus rapide</h1><div class="text-16-white">Si les vérifications passent, la stratégie devient claire : vendre Sar Life et prioriser Future Park.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="benefit-pagination-wrapper"><div class="benefit_circle-wrapper"><div class="benefit_circle _1"></div><div class="benefit_circle _2"></div><div class="benefit_circle _3"></div><div class="benefit_circle _4"></div><div class="benefit_circle _5"></div><div class="benefit_circle _6"></div></div></div></div><div class="sensor-benefit"></div></div></section><section class="section gray s-form test" id="demo"><div class="max-section-wrap"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container test w-container"><div class="maximize-title-wrap"><div class="text-42-regular dark-gradient _w-558 is--dark">Valider la stratégie <span class="span-mob-block">Future Park </span><span class="span-mob-block">maintenant</span></div><div class="mob-spheres-box"><img alt="" class="image-5 _1" loading="eager" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px" src="assets-rebuilt/50b08d4808_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703.webp" srcset="assets-rebuilt/dd0c59dd0d_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703-p-500.webp 500w, assets-rebuilt/1798ea64e9_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703-p-800.webp 800w, assets-rebuilt/50b08d4808_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703.webp 1092w"/><img alt="" class="image-5 _2" loading="eager" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 727.9921875px, 940px" src="assets-rebuilt/11b7ad783e_683f396c4fa03852607779a7_01.webp" srcset="assets-rebuilt/a148dc42d9_683f396c4fa03852607779a7_01-p-500.webp 500w, assets-rebuilt/203050dfa2_683f396c4fa03852607779a7_01-p-800.webp 800w, assets-rebuilt/f1b700cafa_683f396c4fa03852607779a7_01-p-1080.webp 1080w, assets-rebuilt/11b7ad783e_683f396c4fa03852607779a7_01.webp 1200w"/><img alt="" class="image-5 _3" loading="eager" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px" src="assets-rebuilt/98e8672eb8_682b4b46e1ccca4e05aef21a_Group%201020.webp" srcset="assets-rebuilt/fd72cd0d34_682b4b46e1ccca4e05aef21a_Group%201020-p-500.png 500w, assets-rebuilt/98e8672eb8_682b4b46e1ccca4e05aef21a_Group%201020.webp 1092w"/></div></div><div class="form-section-wrap"><div class="form-round-wrap"><div class="div-block-26"><div class="text-42-regular _3-n-1" text-split="">avec une<br/>vérification terrain.<br/></div></div><div class="form-center w-form"><form class="form-2" data-name="Schedule a Demo" data-wf-element-id="d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7908" data-wf-page-id="6824431ce2fd7f3c75768a4d" id="wf-form-Schedule-a-Demo" method="get" name="wf-form-Schedule-a-Demo"><div class="h1 white">Demander la vérification</div><div class="fields-wrap flex"><input class="field-item w-input" data-name="Name 9" id="Name-9" maxlength="256" name="Name-9" placeholder="Name" required="" type="text"/><input class="field-item w-input" data-name="Company 8" id="Company-8" maxlength="256" name="Company-8" placeholder="Company" required="" type="text"/><input class="field-item w-node-d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c790e-75768a4d w-input" data-name="E Mail 8" id="E-mail-8" maxlength="256" name="E-mail-8" placeholder="E-mail" required="" type="email"/></div><div class="form-submit-wrap gap-yes"><input class="btn-yellow w-button" data-wait="Please wait..." id="w-node-d423f57f-f2a3-b8da-feae-90e9156c7910-75768a4d" type="submit" value="Submit"/><div class="text-12-regular _w-193 center">En envoyant ce formulaire, vous demandez une<br/> <a class="link-underlined" href="assets-rebuilt/abc9d0368f_privacy-policy.html">vérification privée </a>du bien, des frais et de la disponibilité réelle.</div></div></form><div class="success-message w-form-done"><div class="text-block-4">Merci.  <br/>Nous revenons vers vous  <br/>rapidement.</div></div><div class="w-form-fail"><div>Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form.</div></div></div><img alt="" class="round-bg" loading="lazy" src="assets-rebuilt/8fa86d454c_682b49dcfef76254e7fdaf71_form.svg"/><img alt="" class="round-right" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px" src="assets-rebuilt/98e8672eb8_682b4b46e1ccca4e05aef21a_Group%201020.webp" srcset="assets-rebuilt/fd72cd0d34_682b4b46e1ccca4e05aef21a_Group%201020-p-500.png 500w, assets-rebuilt/98e8672eb8_682b4b46e1ccca4e05aef21a_Group%201020.webp 1092w"/><img alt="" class="round-left" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px" src="assets-rebuilt/50b08d4808_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703.webp" srcset="assets-rebuilt/dd0c59dd0d_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703-p-500.webp 500w, assets-rebuilt/1798ea64e9_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703-p-800.webp 800w, assets-rebuilt/50b08d4808_682b4b0f00d02d697d098058_703.webp 1092w"/></div></div></div><div class="sensor-maximize"></div></div></section><section class="section linear-gradient" id="footer"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container _2 w-container"><div class="footer-wrap" data-w-id="47b6751d-a4b8-8131-316a-4443685d5414"><div class="footer-top"><div class="text-32-caps _w-20" id="w-node-_47b6751d-a4b8-8131-316a-4443685d5416-685d5412">3-in-1 tool for real estate developers.</div><div class="div-block"><a class="text-16-caps white link" href="#design-section">design</a><a class="text-16-caps white link" href="#estimate-section">estimate</a><a class="text-16-caps white link" href="#shop-section">shop</a><a class="text-16-caps white link" href="#benefit">benefits</a><div class="footer_slot-local"><a class="en-esp without-bg w-in